Summary.valueString: The document promotes Teladoc, a service that allows users to consult with doctors via phone or video, avoiding long wait times at urgent care or ER. It highlights the convenience of accessing licensed physicians for non-emergency conditions like flu, bronchitis, and more, from anywhere, for free. Contact options include visiting Teladoc.com, calling 1-800-TELADOC, or downloading the app.
